quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  12,36,"Sukaa…ďe …ói…óo naatidi e makko ka kaso. Go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe wi'i: \"Min mi hoy…óii hoore-am mi…óo siiwa sanngara\". Oya kadi wi': \"Min mi hoy…óii hoore-am mi…óo ronndii ka hoore-am cobbal, colli no √Īaama e maggal\". Humpitii men firo …óin, menen men yi'ii ma jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"
  12,37,"O maaki: \"√Ďaametee mo wona…óon okkoreede on aratah on si wanaa mi humpitay on firo mun ado o arde on. ∆äum mo'on ko jeyee…óum e ko Joomi am anndini lam. Min mi …óalii diina yim…ďe …ďe gom…óinaa Alla, hara kam…ďe e fii laakara ko …ďe yeddu…ďe"
  12,38,"Jokku-mi diina baabiraa…ďe am …ďen: Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba. Haananaa men nde men kafidata e Alla hay e huunde. ∆äum ko jeyaa…óum e …ďural Alla e dow amen e hoore yim…ďe …ďen; kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe yettataa"
  12,39,"Ko onon yo wondii…ďe am …ói…óo ka kaso! E ko rewetee…ói sertu…ói …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, kaa ko Alla Gooto Foolu…óo on"
  12,40,"On alah e rewde gaanin Makko, si wanah in…óe …óe innu…óon …óum, onon e baabiraa…ďe mon, Alla jippinanaali …óen hujja. √Ďaawoore nden alanah si wanaa Alla. O yamirii wata on rewu si wanaa Kanko. Ko …óum …óum woni diina √Īii…ďuka kan; kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe anndaa"
  12,41,"Ko onon yo wondii…ďe am …ói…óo ka kaso! Go…ó…óo e mo'on yarnay koohoo mun on sanngara; oya on, o fetee, colli …óin √Īaama ka hoore makko. Fiyaaku mo lanndi…óon fii mun on √Īaawaama"
  12,42,"O maakani on mo o sikke da…óay e ma…ď…ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo: \"Janto lam ka koohoojo maa on\". Seytaane yejjintini mo jantanagol koohoojo makko on. [Yuusufu] √Īii…ďiti ka kaso yoga e duu…ďi"